Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.07,0:00:18.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who'd have thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.66,0:00:20.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that such a future was in store for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.95,0:00:22.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.58,0:00:25.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Organization's got me.{lit. sabotaged}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.88,0:00:26.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.54,0:00:31.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you mean all of this is also the choice of Steins Gate?{i thought there was no 'the'}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.09,0:00:36.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.59,0:00:37.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was careless...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.35,0:00:39.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,back then...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.64,0:00:43.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,before those two weeks, when it all began.{*TLC "before"?}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.60,0:00:46.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How did I not notice it?{*TLC lit. Should I have noticed it?}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.48,0:00:52.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.24,0:00:55.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll call you again if I make it out alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.32,0:01:00.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,El. Psy. Congroo.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.95,0:01:03.75,SignDerp,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur0.5\fs50\c&HFEFEFE&\pos(644,316)}{01:04}Two weeks ago
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.45,0:01:03.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.04,0:01:05.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wha—
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.37,0:01:10.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Da-Daru? What's with the Hawaiian get-up?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.25,0:01:13.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not Hawaiian.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.67,0:01:15.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's from L.A.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.72,0:01:17.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,L.A...?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.51,0:01:18.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.30,0:01:20.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was just talking about that!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.14,0:01:27.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Feyris is going to be a contestant{*returning champion?} in a Rainet{*however this was spelled in the show} tournament in America.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.14,0:01:28.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She asked us if we wanted to go with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.52,0:01:29.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you're saying...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.81,0:01:33.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the United States is requesting the aid of Hououin Kyouma?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.36,0:01:36.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Still a faggot{12-year-old}, I see. Sage.{The first one is "chuu-ni byou". TL it however it was TLed in the show}{don't remember}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.28,0:01:43.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Kurisu messaged me!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.79,0:01:45.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She says...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.25,0:01:49.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,she's doing some important{*} research right now and wants us to join her.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.50,0:01:53.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like Kurisu wants to see you, Okarin.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.46,0:01:53.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.26,0:01:55.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.72,0:01:58.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"You don't have to bring Okabe with you, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.38,0:02:01.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to meet him, okay?"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.64,0:02:04.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's "Hot 'n Cold" if I ever saw it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.56,0:02:10.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a good idea for the Future Gadget Lab to get a start on global expansion.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.86,0:02:13.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okarin is like that too, isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.69,0:02:17.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,America?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.36,0:02:19.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Make sure you never come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.11,0:02:20.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bring souvenirs!{kawaii}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.91,0:02:23.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure! What do you want, Moeka?
