Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.65,0:03:38.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm kind of a big deal{* i have no fucking clue, make something up}! Do you understand? Do you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.86,0:03:39.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyouma...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.45,0:03:46.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That damned Organization.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.83,0:03:50.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't expect them to have joined forces with the U.S. to try to catch me—
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.00,0:03:52.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You haven't changed, Okabe.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.79,0:03:56.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okarin?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.63,0:03:59.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Kurisu, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.30,0:04:02.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who do we have here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.43,0:04:04.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My assistant with the hard-on for experiments, Christina.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.64,0:04:05.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not your assistant!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.80,0:04:10.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you were an agent of the Organization at first.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.93,0:04:13.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Epic fail. Saged, reported, called the cops.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.60,0:04:15.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Still a channer I see. Sage.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.02,0:04:15.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.27,0:04:18.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quit your blabbering and let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.94,0:04:23.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it. Don't tell me you're driving—
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.45,0:04:24.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there a problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.41,0:04:25.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rukako, dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.74,0:04:26.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.66,0:04:27.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Call a taxi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.25,0:04:39.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.51,0:04:50.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you panting as if you've been running behind us?{as in, he's pretending}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.35,0:04:55.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.52,0:04:56.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The taxi fare.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.44,0:04:57.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.23,0:04:59.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You—{*what was she going to call him?}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.11,0:05:00.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyouma!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.23,0:05:01.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Feyris!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.19,0:05:05.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I booked you a hotel and everything! Why did you cancel the booking?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.20,0:05:09.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't have the Organization know my whereabouts in advance.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.87,0:05:12.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you mean the seven kings of North America are...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.41,0:05:14.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.71,0:05:16.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seventh Philosophy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.21,0:05:19.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A Japanese-American war already?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.25,0:05:23.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed. But we must avoid these meaningless fights.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.46,0:05:24.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.22,0:05:28.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If necessary, I'll use the secrets of the desert nacht!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.14,0:05:30.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.30,0:05:32.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you telling me you already mastered that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.43,0:05:37.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's time!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.06,0:05:39.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,8,770 km from home, I hereby proclaim,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.02,0:05:45.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Until this body is destroyed and my soul reaches Valhalla,{Timer: till sono toki made}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.36,0:05:48.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I shall fight on the fields of Ragnarok!"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.38,0:06:04.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You sure have a nice place for an assistant.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.96,0:06:07.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can stay here until you find another place to stay.{*TLC}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.05,0:06:10.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't just go in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.22,0:06:12.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't just drink my stuff!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.27,0:06:15.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's asleep!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.64,0:06:20.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Hello, this is Julie Wood.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.90,0:06:22.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This scene is so familiar.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.94,0:06:26.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It really feels just like old times!{It's about how all 5 of them are sitting just like they did in the lab}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.19,0:06:28.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You really like being in that lab, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.70,0:06:32.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How's life here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.66,0:06:35.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.24,0:06:38.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't write down the theory of the time machine, did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.46,0:06:42.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you mean that thing about the parallel world line stuff you told me about earlier?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.92,0:06:48.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just that there might be others with memories of the other world lines apart from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.59,0:06:52.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to worry. All I remember is
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.47,0:06:55.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that you saved me at the radio building.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.97,0:07:00.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I wandered around, looking for you to express my gratitude, before eventually finding you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.06,0:07:00.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.81,0:07:04.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you absolutely sure you don't remember anything else?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.65,0:07:07.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.57,0:07:09.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay then.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.33,0:07:16.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.70,0:07:18.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? You found it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.42,0:07:31.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.43,0:07:39.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a motel!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.52,0:07:41.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.19,0:07:42.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.35,0:07:45.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you just going to abandon us here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.23,0:07:49.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't find a better place for you with your budget.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.28,0:07:54.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Motels are where {*}aliens start possessing people!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.87,0:08:00.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's where madmen wearing hockey masks attack people!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.66,0:08:03.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you really confusing fact and fiction?{This is likely a 2ch line. Localize to taste.}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.33,0:08:04.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maximum autism.{Kinda late for that now.}{likewise}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.71,0:08:09.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know those things only happen in movies...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.76,0:08:12.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I really {\i1}am{\i0} scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.17,0:08:17.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I suppose I shouldn't let Mayuri and Urushibara sleep here alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.14,0:08:20.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayushii will sleep with Okarin, so it's fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.56,0:08:23.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I used to sleep in Okarin's room all the time when I was little.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.98,0:08:26.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In his room?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.27,0:08:28.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just what are you imagining?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.52,0:08:30.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was only when we were little, she said.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.99,0:08:32.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so embarrassing.{as in, he's feeling embarassed by her childishness}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.40,0:08:33.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.65,0:08:36.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, I won't let the girls sleep in your room!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.24,0:08:41.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, Urushibara... is a boy too, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.12,0:08:42.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.20,0:08:45.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right then. I'll stay here too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.54,0:08:48.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, Okabe and Hashida in one room, Mayuri and me in another.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.46,0:08:51.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be by myself?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.51,0:08:52.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.01,0:08:56.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine, Hashida can be in one room, me and Mayuri in another...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.84,0:08:57.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okabe and...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.26,0:09:00.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't mind being with Kyouma.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.18,0:09:03.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But he's a guy.{daga. otoko da.}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.77,0:09:09.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess Miss Makise is forever alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.65,0:09:12.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, Rukako and Mayuri being together is perfectly all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.82,0:09:15.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Suddenly, lesbians. Ha. Ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.57,0:09:16.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Control yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.82,0:09:20.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, if there were lesbians in the next room, then this room would be—
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.03,0:09:21.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{Ah!}{lololololol}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.62,0:09:22.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fuck you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.24,0:09:23.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Okarin.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.83,0:09:24.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.87,0:09:28.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's play rock-paper-scissors to decide who sleeps in the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.13,0:09:36.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.64,0:09:40.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've relinquished my sleeping quarters.{purposefully complicated words}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.76,0:09:43.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Super Hacka is my precious right-hand man, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.68,0:09:44.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You lost at rock-paper-scissors, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.19,0:09:48.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.77,0:09:50.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I was just...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.47,0:10:26.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.27,0:10:28.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you come in for a bit?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.10,0:10:30.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to ask you something.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.82,0:10:36.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is... Diet Dr Pepper!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.74,0:10:39.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you take some back as a souvenir?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.86,0:10:42.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Given the exchange rates right now, it'll be cheaper too.{ou Japan}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.16,0:10:49.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right then. What did you want to ask me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.58,0:10:52.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Intel on the Organization? Or could it be...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.29,0:10:53.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're just gonna make jokes, then get out.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.96,0:10:59.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I remember being told that once before.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.26,0:11:00.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Once before"?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.30,0:11:03.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Another place. Another world line.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.64,0:11:04.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.56,0:11:05.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I wanted to ask you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.22,0:11:10.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a little skeptical about this "other world lines" thing you've told me about.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.31,0:11:15.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But just like you said, I see things in my dreams that never really happened to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.53,0:11:17.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.11,0:11:21.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cheering you up on a bridge in Akihabara.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.28,0:11:26.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Working up a storm writing up some theory on a whiteboard.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.08,0:11:31.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sewing your lab coat in the darkness somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.96,0:11:36.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So some fragments of your memories are still left behind, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.34,0:11:37.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So all of that really happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.09,0:11:42.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, now. Answering that question is extraordinarily difficult, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.30,0:11:48.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To the you in {\i1}this{\i0} world line, it might be all right to say those are just your dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.10,0:11:51.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But... they {\i1}did{\i0} happen in the other world lines.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.89,0:11:52.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.69,0:11:54.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.19,0:11:56.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.69,0:12:00.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, tell me something.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.07,0:12:00.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.49,0:12:05.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... There's one more weird dream I saw.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.24,0:12:09.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You and I, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.33,0:12:10.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.16,0:12:12.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.42,0:12:16.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong? Need to go pee-pee?{not necessarily that childishly spoken, but still not normal. Hence her reaction}{lol}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.21,0:12:19.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You perv!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.30,0:12:31.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okarin and Kurisu sure get along, don't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.27,0:12:41.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Game. Set. Match!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.65,0:12:44.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cut over!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.32,0:12:47.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He let his guard down! Feyris won the tournament!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.87,0:12:48.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.70,0:12:53.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Feyris! Feyris! Feyris!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.13,0:13:00.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's a dude, but who cares?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.84,0:13:03.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look how popular you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.68,0:13:13.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Your order of rice omelet.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.60,0:13:17.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.60,0:13:18.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about adding a cute "meow" at the end of your sentences?{gl brainchild}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.61,0:13:21.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do {\i1}I{\i0} have to do that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.86,0:13:27.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Assistant, dear. You are the representative of Japan's maid culture—
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.61,0:13:31.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never agreed to that. Nor do I {\i1}want{\i0} to do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.12,0:13:35.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You need to help out here to pay for your plane ticket.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.25,0:13:37.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's natural for a lab member to cooperate.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.62,0:13:40.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When did anyone pay for my ticket?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.79,0:13:43.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all for one and one for all.{Lab members are one in joy, one in trouble.}{一心同体}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.05,0:13:44.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then you work too!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.84,0:13:47.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seeing how energetic you are,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.39,0:13:50.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you must've had a good night's sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.76,0:13:52.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You looked worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.27,0:13:55.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.81,0:13:58.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was just a bit curious.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.90,0:14:01.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, that's not it either.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.11,0:14:02.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just forget about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.40,0:14:06.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing to gain from remembering other world lines' events.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.11,0:14:08.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.11,0:14:10.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I do plan to forget everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.70,0:14:13.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.68,0:14:30.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry I'm late!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.81,0:14:36.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Suzuha?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.19,0:14:39.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Suzuha!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.65,0:14:49.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why is Suzuha here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.24,0:14:51.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I remember what she said in the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.20,0:14:54.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.49,0:14:57.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Let's meet again... in seven years.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.45,0:15:00.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The time machine hasn't been invented in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.58,0:15:03.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She shouldn't exist for another seven years, when she's actually born.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.80,0:15:08.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But if she's here...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.38,0:15:10.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This world has a time machine too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.47,0:15:14.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Maybe... the third World War too...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.43,0:15:17.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Okabe isn't there?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.56,0:15:24.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I saw him stumbling out of the building.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.02,0:15:30.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Girls! Someone saw him getting into a taxi with a brooding look on his face.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.07,0:15:33.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.12,0:15:35.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nah, he's probably just being himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.08,0:15:38.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kurisu?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.16,0:15:41.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you chased me all the way here, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.25,0:15:44.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So... you're not her?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.33,0:15:45.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.54,0:15:48.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I came here to play in the Rainet tournament,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.00,0:15:52.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and now I'm going with a friend{ who lives here} to Las Vegas.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.97,0:15:53.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.97,0:15:57.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But to chase a girl all the way out here...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.22,0:15:59.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,she must be really important to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.39,0:16:01.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The girl who looks just like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.85,0:16:06.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. She's a precious friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.90,0:16:09.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't know where she is now?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.36,0:16:12.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not right now.{He lit. says "She's not here now." but that sounds like he's saying she's dead, which is not what he means in the original .jp}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.45,0:16:15.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'll be able to see her again in seven years.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.41,0:16:17.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.53,0:16:20.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ooh. That's so romantic.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.70,0:16:26.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had a fortune that said I'd get married and have a baby in seven years, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.30,0:16:29.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.46,0:16:31.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, never mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.89,0:16:37.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry for taking so much of your time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.85,0:16:40.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all. It was fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.81,0:16:41.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See you around!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.40,0:16:48.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.62,0:16:57.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Seven more years.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.08,0:17:06.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I wouldn't believe that either.{kieta tokoro de, wakaru hazu ga nai... ka?}{he means that she's gone, so that girl who's not her "yet" has no reason to believe his nonsense}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.71,0:17:13.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Remaining change: 67 cents.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.92,0:17:14.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Battery: Dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.22,0:17:17.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How the hell am I gonna get back?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.93,0:17:24.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That was two hours ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.07,0:17:33.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kurisu...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.75,0:17:47.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.04,0:17:50.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not going to lose here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.04,0:17:54.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the mad scientist
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.21,0:17:56.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hououin Kyouma!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.98,0:18:06.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not going to...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.02,0:18:09.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.02,0:18:14.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to tell...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.95,0:18:17.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,her...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.78,0:18:21.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me what?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.54,0:18:33.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now I'm hallucinating.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.46,0:18:35.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you going on about?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.13,0:18:39.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is undoubtedly the reality being reflected in your retinas and interpreted by your brain.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.18,0:18:42.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I finally found you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.27,0:18:51.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're going to save someone, you should at least make sure you have enough gas first.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.48,0:18:53.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not my fault! I was in a hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.90,0:18:55.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about your phone?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.61,0:18:57.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lame.{occhogochoe}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.44,0:18:58.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A phone with no battery.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.86,0:19:00.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sixty seven cents.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.53,0:19:03.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were lying knocked out on the highway!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.33,0:19:05.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to hear that coming from {\i1}you!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.87,0:19:07.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This was important, though.{I'm sorry, but I'm out of synonyms.}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.58,0:19:11.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was chasing after someone I thought I knew from way back.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.46,0:19:12.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone you knew?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.92,0:19:13.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.17,0:19:15.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.09,0:19:19.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you ran away because of what I said.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.76,0:19:20.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.01,0:19:23.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.89,0:19:25.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.35,0:19:27.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.97,0:19:29.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I said I'd forget everything...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.10,0:19:31.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.98,0:19:34.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't just brush it off like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.07,0:19:37.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's really, really important to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.61,0:19:38.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Important?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.74,0:19:39.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.11,0:19:42.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just that...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.95,0:19:43.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.78,0:19:47.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There was one more weird dream I had.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.37,0:19:49.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just can't stop thinking about that one.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.54,0:19:53.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's kinda like it's too realistic for a dream, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.21,0:19:54.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's real.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.38,0:19:57.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I said, it's real...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.96,0:19:59.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.21,0:20:00.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.63,0:20:03.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In another world line, I told you that I loved you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.35,0:20:07.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I {\i1}do{\i0} love you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.77,0:20:11.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.98,0:20:16.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're awful.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.11,0:20:21.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must've spent a lot of time with me in your other world lines,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.15,0:20:27.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but to me, everything I did in those world lines is just a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.58,0:20:29.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's hard to take all of this in.{THAT'S WHAT SHE SAID}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.13,0:20:39.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have an ability called "Reading Steiner."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.59,0:20:43.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've retained my memories of all the other world lines.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.93,0:20:45.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is why I know...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.51,0:20:48.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the three weeks that I spent with you...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.64,0:20:52.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it was much, much longer than three weeks...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.77,0:20:55.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know this {\i1}because{\i0} I was with you for so long.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.19,0:21:00.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter which world line, what time, or where I am,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.98,0:21:02.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll always love you.{He says this in past tense, but it makes more sense to be in present future}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.28,0:21:07.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll say it one more time, Makise Kurisu.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.66,0:21:09.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.79,0:21:12.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.91,0:21:14.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, at this very instant,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.62,0:21:17.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,how do you think of me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.50,0:21:20.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.46,0:21:25.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you really want to know?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.16,0:21:50.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Close your eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.87,0:21:51.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{ED}
