Dialogue: 1,0:22:10.51,0:22:17.19,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}is a basic matter of little glamor to you
Dialogue: 1,0:22:17.19,0:22:22.27,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}Imprisoned in the past we lament the future
Dialogue: 1,0:22:22.27,0:22:28.32,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}and not even miscalculating a single speck of dust would be permissible
Dialogue: 1,0:22:28.32,0:22:34.33,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}Our dreams stretching out as infinity and the future we imagine
Dialogue: 1,0:22:34.33,0:22:40.25,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}are a vain privilege we allowed ourselves
Dialogue: 1,0:22:40.25,0:22:46.42,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}Finity is what the two hands of the clock point out
Dialogue: 1,0:22:46.42,0:22:51.01,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}forcing us to make cruel decisions in life
Dialogue: 1,0:22:51.01,0:22:53.30,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}Hacking to the Gate
Dialogue: 1,0:22:53.30,0:23:00.23,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}Now I cross world lines with every passing second
Dialogue: 1,0:23:00.23,0:23:05.19,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}and wish to protect your smile
Dialogue: 1,0:23:05.19,0:23:12.07,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}Now I am again sucked into a time loop as a solitary observer
Dialogue: 1,0:23:12.07,0:23:18.41,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}where sadness holds no sway
